            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200515_Corley_Lawrence_Q3</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What goes into organizing so many volunteers to come together to rebuild the Roaring Fork Baptist Church?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 3</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:30:57"
                            endTime="00:33:01">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200515_Corley_Lawrence_Q4</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>How did you, the pastor, and the congregation decide upon the space needs? What were they looking for in terms of space? Did they want to expand?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 4</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:33:01"
                            endTime="00:41:55">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200515_Corley_Lawrence_Q5</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>How do you interact with the congregation during this time? Did you share your testimony with them?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 5</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:41:55"
                            endTime="00:44:05">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200515_Corley_Lawrence_Q6</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>How did the church finance the building materials?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 6</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:44:05"
                            endTime="00:48:17">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200515_Corley_Lawrence_Q7</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>After finishing the construction, what was it like for the congregation to worship there?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 7</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:48:17"
                            endTime="00:57:30">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200515_Corley_Lawrence_Q8</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>This was the 37th church that you team has built, can you compare this experience with the others?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 8</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:57:30"
                            endTime="01:00:45">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20200515_Corley_Lawrence_Q9</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
